This project is a Qt6 QML reimplementation of MacSlow's Cairo-Clock,
rewritten to run on modern Linux systems without deprecated dependencies.

The original clock face themes are redistributed under their original
GPL v2 license. Additional themes included in the favorites folder
were sourced from gnome-look.org and are believed to be GPL v2 compatible.
If you are the author of any included theme and have concerns,
please contact the project maintainer.
